Day 216/366✅ challenge 
UBTAN ❤️
For everyday glowing skin ✨
Get instant glowing skin 😍

Ingredients used- 
2 tsp besan 
2 tsp rice powder 
2 tsp Multani mitti 
2 tsp Chandan powder 
1/2 tsp turmeric powder 

Procedure 
In a container add

2 tsp besan 
2 tsp rice powder 
2 tsp Multani mitti 
2 tsp Chandan powder 
1/2 tsp turmeric powder 
and mix well.
Store it for upto 3 months ❤️
To use the UBTAN, take 2 tsp of UBTAN powder 
and 3 tsp of rose water and mix well .
Apply on the face for 15 minutes ⏰ and then wash it off with water 💦 

Benefits 

🟡Skin becomes bright and glowing ✨
🟡 Get glass skin with this face mask!!

Day 242/366✅ challenge 
DIY Rice toner 🤍

Ingredients used 
filtered water 💧 
1/4 cup white rice 🌾🍚
1/4 cup raw milk 🥛 
1/4 cup rose water 🌹💧
Storage bottle 🧴 

Procedure 
1- Wash 1/4 cup raw rice 🌾 thoroughly in 1 cup of water 💧 and drain the water.
2- Soak the washed rice in 1/2 cup of filtered water for 2 hours ⏰.
3- In a bowl add 1/4 cup rice water 🌾💧, 1/ 4 cup raw milk 🥛and 1/4 cup rose water 🌹💧 and mix well.
4- Store  the rice toner in a storage bottle 🧴.
Shake well before use 🧴
✨You can  use this toner twice a day

Benefits 
🟡Gives a healthy glow ✨
🟡 Brightens skin naturally
